review_text:
This is yet another reason why I left IMDb and came here, taking my reviews with me... can't write a bad review about this one either because... reasons.  I don't know, but the mods there were going out of their way to protect this from all criticism.

Anyway this is about a small town girl who makes an 80 glam band... and that is it.  It literally has nothing at all to do with Jem and the Holograms... nothing.

The cartoon rocked, no pun intended, and they took all of that away to make it more meh.
